reviews.review_text: There's no show like this! Redrocks is the only comparable venue in terms of sheer electrical energy hot spots in the Southwestern United States.  Highlights include a Music Never Stopped opener where Bob has not harnessed that aforementioned electrical energy but he soon "gets it right" and his songs are superb in both sets.  Jerry is ON FIRE the whole show and highlights include a SICK (very good) China/RIder, Other One>Goin' Down The Road>Saturday Night.  This recording is stellar and practically incomparable.  Thank you for it!
